findings.message: YVaultAssetProxy.reserveWithdraw(uint256) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#549-574) ignores return value by token.transfer(msg.sender,freedUnderlying + userUnderlying) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#573)
findings.name: unchecked-transfer

findings.message:
Reentrancy in YVaultAssetProxy.reserveWithdraw(uint256) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#549-574):
	External calls:
	- freedUnderlying = vault.withdraw(userShares,address(this),0) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#558)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- _setReserves(localUnderlying - userUnderlying,localShares - userShares) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#564-567)
		- reserveShares = uint128(_newReserveShares) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#689)
	YVaultAssetProxy.reserveShares (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#487) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- YVaultAssetProxy._getReserves() (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#677-679)
	- YVaultAssetProxy._setReserves(uint256,uint256) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#684-690)
	- YVaultAssetProxy.reserveShares (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#487)
	- reserveSupply = localReserveSupply - _amount (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#569)
	YVaultAssetProxy.reserveSupply (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#489) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- YVaultAssetProxy.reserveDeposit(uint256) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#514-545)
	- YVaultAssetProxy.reserveSupply (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#489)
	- YVaultAssetProxy.reserveWithdraw(uint256) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#549-574)
	- _setReserves(localUnderlying - userUnderlying,localShares - userShares) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#564-567)
		- reserveUnderlying = uint128(_newReserveUnderlying) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#688)
	YVaultAssetProxy.reserveUnderlying (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#486) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- YVaultAssetProxy._getReserves() (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#677-679)
	- YVaultAssetProxy._setReserves(uint256,uint256) (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#684-690)
	- YVaultAssetProxy.reserveUnderlying (YVaultAssetProxy.sol#486)
